::Prowl/Rixer::

Prowl recieves IR's order, having finished battling with bots in the holo room just a little while back.

-Ok,- he replies to her, walking out of the room and activating his comm link.

"Orion, can you gather any Maximals around you and meet me in front of the city? We have a Maximal to save."

He nearly bumps into Rixer on his way out, waving for the bot to follow him as he hurries to the exit.
